metadata.name: ambition.
metadata.description:
Collage from a dollar bill. Serial number: B 57939582 D

NFT, 3484 x 3484 px, linked to the physical collage on cardboard, signed with embossing, 29.5 x 29.5 cm. 

The owner of the NFT owns the physical asset. A QR code on the back of the work provides information about its provenance (Etherscan).

The collection "You can’t buy …" consists of 16 one-dollar bills. Each bill was cut by hand and the letters were assembled into new words. By destroying the bills, new values were created.
